	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				If you plan on fighting any number of these, do yourself a favor:  Get a sewing kit.  <BR>
<BR>
By combining two spider silks, you get a silk swatch.  It is impossible to fail making a silk swatch, even if you have 0 skill in tailoring, and swatches are stackable, unlike unwoven silks.  <BR>
<BR>
This will allow you to gain a little tailoring skill (up to 15 or so) with no risk, and keep you from having to continually stop hunting in order to sell off your silks.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
