				I once saw a Queen something Spider in lfay, while I was camping the 3 cutthroat bandits.  It was 12ish but its poison was a lot stronger than a regular giant spider and it hit a lot harder.  Two 13s were able to take it out while taking a fair amount of damage.  It dropped a Pulsating Brood Clotch (magic item) that looked like a venom sac, nobody knew what it was when I asked, but it sold for around 8pp to the vendors.  The queen was KOS.  Never seen one since.
