				Well, if you are poisoned and need it taken off right away, just seek the assistance of a cleric. But it still fades off. I dont really know what this poison does, because I am a cleric, so I just heal it right away. <BR>
<BR>
Also, I have ehhh...kinda bad armor, im a lvl 8 with AC of 174, and I cant take on these spiders on my own, I will usually be running toward the guards when I fight one. They con either White or Yellow to me. <BR>
<BR>
On the subject of the guards killing you, it happens alot. Especially if you are a race that the humans hate. I am an erudite, and apperatnly they hate us =). But they dont kill me to much, I guess killing all those gnolls helped =). Ok thats it, laterz.<BR>
